{"tid":1459454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[塞鐵事宜]代表部分高登會員 反對塞鐵行動","createTime":"2019-08-12T17:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T19:00:33.000Z","uid":49269,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"db54eca384a729d1a4f0ce88fd6db48ab1580d9a","tid":1459454,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"現時夜媽媽  <br />\n果邊人數真係唔多<br />\n但之前同而家望到既意見都係 <br />\n希望唔好塞鐵<br />\n特別經過今日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全世界既新聞都指緊向警狗既時候<br />\n聽日塞鐵又比人彈番去示威者既不合作運動度<br />\n仲少不免又會有衝突 但效果有目共睹 係非常細<br />\n聲音大。。 效果小<br />\n因為政府冇損失 由你民鬥民<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n你塞機場帶黎既經濟損失大過塞鐵  差距係以至少百倍為單位去計  <br />\n<br />\n理由可能仲有千百萬個<br />\n唔係要分化 割蓆<br />\n但希望可以聽下人意見<br />\n唔係下下話各自爬山就我行我素<br />\n<br />\n不分化既精神同力量唔應該咁樣浪費"},{"pid":"b6e93166d87ffce360bd596318954ea29668bb12","tid":1459454,"uid":49269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"聲音細微既小部分高登仔們的深夜心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccddce5c6196073099b675d10684e154eed2c0eb","tid":1459454,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db5bb566b56dbfc530f207695a25e5ca01a4349","tid":1459454,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ee94fff11d058441ce97f3d386abde073cc99d","tid":1459454,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c